text: Fitchburg is a city in Dane County, Wisconsin, United States. The population was 29,609 at the 2020 census. Fitchburg is a suburb of Madison and is part of the Madison Metropolitan Statistical Area. In 1983, Fitchburg became a city. ==References== Category:Cities in Wisconsin Category:Dane County, Wisconsin Category:1983 establishments in the United States Category:20th-century establishments in Wisconsin
